comments.Notes: In Flexxx Our Employees, their families and our community has always been our top priority .Our motive is to keep employees healthy and safe in light of the Covid-19 outbreak that is progressing across India. One month ago, Flex India activated a Crisis Management Team (CMT) led by Richard Hopkins. The India CMT team is constantly monitoring the situation and is committed to providing regular updates and guidance via emails, townhall session, bulletin boards and other communication channels.
